<paragraph id="IFRS07_IG40" base="F95490" principles="no"><paranum>IG40</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 7"/><data name="paranum" value="IG40"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS07_P2082">In the situation described in <xref id="IFRS07_X1198" base="F15835093" href="IFRS07_IG37.dita#IFRS07_IG37">paragraph IG37(c)</xref>, additional disclosure might include:</p><ol id="IFRS07_L0157" base="SL160912" type="lower-alpha"><li><li_value>(a)</li_value> <p id="IFRS07_P2083" base="SL160914">the nature of the security (eg entity name);</p></li><li><li_value>(b)</li_value> <p id="IFRS07_P2084" base="SL160916">the extent of holding (eg 15 per cent of the issued shares);</p></li><li><li_value>(c)</li_value> <p id="IFRS07_P2085" base="SL160918">the effect on profit or loss; and</p></li><li><li_value>(d)</li_value> <p id="IFRS07_P2086" base="SL160920">how the entity hedges the risk.</p></li></ol></body></paragraph>